         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute rend="inline"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00291"/>lieber</salute></opener><p>ich bin mit der <rs type="work" ref="#pmb32512" subtype="implied">Arbeit</rs> fertig
               und in <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>. Erbitte Verkehr!</p><p>z. B. morgen abend <rs ref="#pmb49" type="place">Pfob</rs>?</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>Hugo</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
